quran[110]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Pẽgr be ne Naab ning sẽn sika Gafã A yambã zugã, n pɑ maan-a t'a tar goɑleng ye!"
  18,2,"A yaa tɩrg sẽn na yɩl n bugs ne nang sẽn zabd n yi A nengẽ; la A noog sɩd-kõtb sẽn maan tʋʋm-sõma sũuri, tɩ b tara keoor sẽn be neere."
  18,3,"B yɑɑ paadb ɑ pʋgẽ lɑe-lɑe."
  18,4,"La A bugs neb nins sẽn yeel tɩ Wẽnd tara biigã."
  18,5,"Bãmb mens pa tar bãngr buud ne rẽ; b saam-rãmb me pa talle. Ad gomd ning sẽn yit b noyẽ wã yɩ bedre, ad b sẽn yetã pa yɩ rẽnda zĩri."
  18,6,"Lɑ tõe tɩ fo wa pogend f meng b poorẽ, b sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne gom-kãngã sũ-sãɑg keelem."
  18,7,"Ad Tõnd maana sẽn be tẽngã zugã tɩ yɑɑ faas-teed ne-ɑ sẽn na yɩl n zarb-b n ges ned ning sẽn yɩɩda ne tʋʋm sõmblem."
  18,8,"Lɑ Tõnd na n mɑɑnɑ sẽn be a zugã tɩ lebg zĩ-peen-dɑɑgɑ."
  18,9,"Bɩ fo tẽedame tɩ vadgã rãmbã la (Raƙɩɩm) neb nins yʋy sẽn gʋls walgẽ wã ra yɩɩme n yaa yel-soalem Tõnd tagmasã sʋk lɑ?"
  18,10,"Wakat ning rao-sãmbã sẽn wa n kẽng n tɩ sool vadgẽ wã, n yeele: "" d Soaba! Kõ tõnd yolsg sẽn yi Fo nengẽ la F segl tõnd n kãndag d yellã pʋga''."
  18,11,"Tɩ Tõnd na n lims b tʋbã vɑdgã pʋgẽ yʋʋm wʋsgo."
  18,12,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd vʋʋg-b sẽn na yɩl n bãng sul a yiibã sẽn kɩɩsd tɑɑbã sẽn yɩɩda minim ne b sẽn zĩnd be wã sõore."
  18,13,"Tõnd togsda foom b kibarã ne sɩda, ad b yaa ra-sãmb sẽn kõ sɩd ne b Soabã tɩ Tõnd paas-b kãndagre."
  18,14,"La D keng b sũyã, b sẽn wa n yik n yeele: ""tõnd Soabã la sɑɑs lɑ tẽng Soabã, d ka na n bool soɑb zẽng lɑe tɩ pa Yẽ ye, tõnd sã n mɑɑn rẽ, ɑd tõnd yeelɑ gomd sẽn zãr ne sɩdɑ."
  18,15,"Bãmbã sẽn yaa tõnd nebã rɩka soab zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde, la yaa bõe tɩ b pa nɑ n wa ne tikr sẽn yaɑ vẽeneg b tũudmẽ wã, la ãnd n yɩɩd wẽgd ne ned ning sẽn wãaga zĩri n rogl Wẽnde?"
  18,16,"La y sẽn welg n bas-b ne b sẽn tũud bũmb ning tɩ pa Wẽndã, bɩ y sool n kẽng vadgẽ wã, tɩ y Soɑbã na sãeeg A yolsgã y yĩng la A sεgl yol-yol n kõ-ya y yellẽ wã."
  18,17,"La fo yãtɑ wĩntoogã t'a sã n puki, a kɩlldɑme n bas b vɑdgã rɩtg wεεngẽ, la a sã n lʋɩtẽ la a sẽn basd-b n kɩll goabg wεεngẽ, tɩ bãmb be zĩ-yɑlengẽ vɑdgẽ wã. Wãndã yaa sẽn yi Wẽnd yel-soɑlmã pʋgẽ. Wẽnd sẽn kãnd a soabɑ, yẽ n rɩkd so-tɩrga, la A sẽn menes a soabã, fo kõn n tol n paam lall-n-taag sẽn nɑ n kãnd-a ye."
  18,18,"Lɑ fo tẽedɑme tɩ b neeme, tɩ b yaool n yaa sẽn gõe. Tɩ Tõnd leebd-b rɩtg wεεngẽ la goabg wεεngẽ, tɩ b baagã tẽeg a kɑrs ɑ yiibã noorẽ wã. Fo sã n lik n yã-ba fo na lebg n wudg n bɑs-bɑ, f nɑ tɑll pelen-yɩk me ne-bɑ."
  18,19,"La yaa woto la Tõnd yik-ba tɩ b nɑ n sogs taaba; yεt n zĩnd b sʋkã n yeele: "" yaa sõor wãn la yãmb sẽn zĩndã?"" La b yeele: "" tõnd zĩndɑ raar maa rɑɑr pεdgɑ"". La b kẽer yeele: "" yãmb Soabã n yɩɩd minim ne rasem ning sõor yãmb sẽn zĩndã, bɩ y tʋms yãmb ned a yembr ne yãmb ligd koεεng-kãngã t'a kẽng tẽngã pʋgẽ n tɩ ges rɩɩb ning yɩleng sẽn yɩɩdɑ bɩ ɑ wɑ ne rɩtl sẽn yi be, la ɑ maan lɑm-lɑm tɩ ned ra bãng yãmb yellã ye."
  18,20,"Ad b sã n bãng yãmb zĩigɑ, b na n loba yãmb n kʋ maa b lebs yãmb b dĩinẽ wã, lɑ y kõn n tol n tɩlg rẽ poorẽ lae."
  18,21,"La yaa woto la Tõnd mɑɑn tɩ b yẽnd-ba, sẽn na yɩl tɩ nebã bãng tɩ Wẽnd pʋlengã yaa sɩda, lɑ Dũni wã yikrã sik ka be a pʋgẽ ye. Lɑ wɑkɑt ning nebã sẽn wa n maan no-koeemd b yellã zugã, b yeelɑme: ""me-y meeng b zugu, ɑd b Soɑbã n yɩɩd minim ne b yellã"", la zut-rãmbã sẽn yɑɑ zɩtbã yeele: "" d na n rɩka b zĩigã n mɑɑn misri""."
  18,22,"B na n yeelɑme: "" b yɑɑ tãabo, tɩ b baagã paas naase"". B leb n yetɑme: "" b yɑɑ nu, tɩ b yoob soɑbã yaɑ b baagã"", n gomd b sẽn ka mi. B leb n yetɑme: "" b yɑɑ b yopoe tɩ b baagã paas nii"". Yeele: "" mam Soabã n yɩɩd minim ne b sõorã, ka mi bãmbã sõorã rẽnda bilf bala"". Bɩ f ra maan no-koeemd bãmbã yellã zug rẽnda no-koeemd sẽn yɑɑ lεngɑ, la f ra sok b yellã ned baa a yembr bãmbã pʋgẽ ye."
  18,23,"(La sã n dat n maan bũmb bɩ) f ra wa yeele: "" mam na n maana woto beoog ye""."
  18,24,"Rallame tɩ f paase:""tɩ Wẽnd sã n sake"". La tẽeg f Soabã yʋʋr tɩ fo sã n yĩmi, la yeele: "" tõe tɩ m Soabã kãndg maam n tʋg sor sẽn yaa tɩrga""."
  18,25,"La b zĩnda b vadgẽ wã yʋʋm kobs-tã tɩ b paas (yʋʋm) a wae."
  18,26,"Yeele: ""Wẽnd n yɩɩd minim ne b sẽn zĩndã sõore, Yẽ n so sɑasã la tẽngã yel-soondse. A nenem pa tar to, A wʋmb pa tar to! Ad bãmbã pa tar lall-n-taag zẽng sẽn pɑ Yẽ ye, A leb n ka lagemd A naamã pʋgẽ ned baa a yembr ye."
  18,27,"Lɑ f karem bũmb ning b sẽn tʋms tɩ tɩ wa fo nengẽ wã sẽn yi fo Soɑbã Gɑfẽ wã, toeemd pa tõe n toeem A goamã ye, fo le kõn n paam relleg zĩig zẽng sẽn ka Yẽ ye."
  18,28,"La maan sugr n naag f meng ne neb nins sẽn kot b Soabã yibeoog la zaabrã, n tʋll A yardã (a nengã yãabo / yel-sõmdã). La ra wa zʋʋg f nin a yiibã n gãndg-b n rɑt dũni wã faas-teedã ye. La ra wa tũ ned ning Tõnd sẽn yẽd ɑ soɑb sũur t'a yaa yam yaal-yaal soaba n yi Tõnd yʋʋrã tẽegre, n leb n pʋgd a yõorã yamleoog t'a yellã yeebe."
  18,29,"Lɑ yeele: ""sɩdã lɑ sẽn yi yãmb Soabã nengẽ wã, ned ning sẽn tʋllɑ bɩ a kõ sɩda, sẽn rata me bɩ a kɩfle"" ad Tõnd sεgla Bugum wẽgdbã yĩngɑ, t'a lalgã gũbg-ba, la b sã n wa baood yũubu, b yũnugd-b lame ne koom sẽn yaa wala rãngo, n gãogd nensẽ, bõn-yũudi yɩ wẽnga, zĩndig zĩig me yɩ wẽnga."
  18,30,"Ad neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩdã la b tʋm tʋʋm sõma wã, ad Tõnd pa yeebd ned ning sẽn maneg a tʋʋmd keoor ye."
  18,31,"Bãmb rãmbã tara arzãn tɩ kʋɩls zoet a tẽngrã, tɩ b nɑgsd-b beenẽ ne zũy sẽn yɑɑ sãnem la b yeelgd fut sẽn yɑɑ kõoda sẽn yaɑ fu-sɑɑlɑ (harɩɩr) sẽn yaa faas lɑ tɑgdo, tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn kɩll ɑ pʋgẽ gat zutu, ad yel-sõmd yɩ neema tɩ zĩndig zĩig me be neere."
  18,32,"La rɩk bilgr n wĩnig-b raop a yiibu, Tõnd maana sib pʋt a yiib n kõ b yiibã yembre, la D gũbg pʋt a yiibã ne tɑmɑr-tɩɩse, la D ning kood pʋt a yiibã sʋka."
  18,33,"Pʋt a yiibã fãa woma womb tεkẽ b pa boog bɑɑ fʋɩ ye, tɩ Tõnd pusg kʋɩlg pʋt a yiibã sʋka."
  18,34,"Lɑ ɑ le tar tɩ-biis ɑ tɑɑbɑ, la a yeel a tũud-n-taagã n sõsd ne-a: ""mam yɩɩda foom ne arzεka, n leb n yɩɩd foo ne neb sõor lɑ zɩslem."
  18,35,"La a kẽ a pʋʋgã pʋg tɩ yẽnda yaa sẽn wẽg a menga, ɑ yeelɑme: ""mam pa tẽed tɩ wãnde na n sɑame lae;"
  18,36,"m leb n pa tagsd tɩ Dũni wã me na n yikame, lɑ baa tɩ b sã n lebs mɑɑm m Soabã nengẽ, m na n tɩ mika sõmã sẽn yɩɩd mam pʋʋgã yεsɑ""."
  18,37,"A tũud-n-taagã yeel-a lɑme n sõsd ne-a: "" rẽ yĩnga fo mɑɑndɑ sõm-zɩɩlem ne Naab ning sẽn naana foom n yi tomẽ wã, rẽ poorẽ ne mani, rẽ poorẽ t'A naan foom tɩ f yɑɑ raoa?"""
  18,38,"La sã n yaa ne maam, yaa Wẽnd la mam Soabã, m kõn n maan lagem-n-taar ne m Soɑbã baa ɑ ye."
  18,39,"Fo sẽn wa n kẽ f pʋʋgẽ wã, fo sã n da yeelame:"" ad yaa sẽn tɑ ne Wẽnd rɑɑb la woto! Pãng ka be rẽnda ne Wẽnde"". Fo sã n neeme tɩ mam pa tɑ foo ne arzεk la koamba,"
  18,40,"Ad mɑm Soabã tõe n kõo maam sõblem sẽn yɩɩd fo pʋʋgã, la A tʋms fo pʋʋgẽ wã gεεl sẽn yi saasẽ wã t'a lebg zĩ-peell n salsd nɑo."
  18,41,"Maa a koomã lebg zulung tɩ fo ka tõe n bao-a n paam ye""."
  18,42,"Tɩ sãangã gubg a tɩ-biisã t'ɑ wɑ bɑɑs n pãbd nug-poak yẽ arzεkã a sẽn kẽes a pʋgẽ wã bõne, tɩ pʋʋgã kao n lʋɩ a yẽgã zutu. Tɩ yẽ yetẽ: "" kɑto m bãngẽ n rag n ka maanẽ lagem-n-taar ne mam Soabã baa yembre""!"
  18,43,"Tɩ zãma ka zĩnd n na n sõng-a n yi Wẽnd nɑngã ye; ɑ pa tõog n sõng a meng me ye."
  18,44,"Zĩ-kãensã zĩigẽ fãɑgd yɑɑ Wẽnd ɑ yembre, Yẽnda rolb n yɩɩd sõmblem lɑ bɑɑs neere."
  18,45,"La rɩk bilgr n wĩnig-b dũni wã vɩɩmã yalẽ, a yaa wala koom Tõnd sẽn sik-a saasẽ wã tɩ tẽngã bõn-tobd fugumd ne-ɑ; rẽ loogr poorẽ t'a wɑ lebg zeend tɩ sebgã yelgd-ɑ, lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yaa Tõod ne bũmbã fãa."
  18,46,"Arzεkã la kom-ribli wã yaa dũni wã faas-teedo, la ad tʋʋm sõmã wã n yɩɩd sõmblem ne keoob fo Soabã nengẽ, la b yɩɩd sõmblem me tẽeb pʋgẽ."
  18,47,"Lɑ tẽeg raar ning Tõnd sẽn na n kẽnes tãmsã tɩ fo ne tẽngã t'a yaa sẽn puk zãngɑ, tɩ Tõnd tigim-b n pa bɑs b ned baa a yembr ye."
  18,48,"Tɩ b tall-b n tɩ bɑll ne fo Soabã nengẽ rulg-rulgɑ: "" ad yãmb waa Tõnd nengẽ wala Tõnd sẽn ra naan yãmb rãeenemã; yãmb yaool n rag n sãmbdame tɩ D kõn n tol n maan sεk ne yãmb ye."
  18,49,"Tɩ b rɩglg (tʋʋmã) gafo, tɩ fo ne nin-wẽnsã sẽn be pelen-yɩk pʋgẽ ne bũmb ning sẽn be gafẽ wã, la b yetẽ: ""yaa tõnd wɩɩbdo! Yaa bõe me gɑf lɑ woto n pa basd sẽn paood maa sẽn waoog rẽndame t'a gũbg-a?"" Tɩ b mik b sẽn tʋmã tɩ be beenẽ, la fo Soabã pa wẽgd ned baa a yembr ye."
  18,50,"Lɑ tẽeg Tõnd sẽn wa n yeel malεgsã: "" maan-y a Adam suguudu"", tɩ b maan suguudã, rẽnda a ɭblɩɩs bɑl sẽn dɑ yɑɑ zĩnã, t'ɑ zãgs a Soabã saglgã, rẽ yĩngã yãmb na n rɩk-a lame ne a koambã n maan lall-n-taas tɩ ka Maam, tɩ b yaool n yaa yãmb bεεba? Ad wẽgdbã tedgr yɩ wẽnga."
  18,51,"Mam ka mɑɑn-b (a ɭblɩɩs ne a koambã) kaset saasã la tẽngã naanegẽ, b pa yɩt kaset ne b mensã nɑɑneg me, la Mam pa yɩ n na n rɩk menesdbã tɩ yaa sõngdb ye."
  18,52,"Tẽeg raar ning A sẽn na n yeel-ba: "" bool-y Mam lagem-n-taas nins yãmb sẽn da yẽgemdã wε,"". Tɩ b na n bool-b tɩ b ka sak b yĩng ye, tɩ Tõnd mɑɑn hɑlkr zĩig tɩ b nɑɑg tɑɑb ɑ pʋgẽ."
  18,53,"Tɩ nin-wẽnsã yãnd Bugmã ne bãng-n-wãak tɩ bãmb na n lʋɩɩ a pʋgẽ, la b pa paam põsgr zĩig n nɑ n yi-a ye."
  18,54,"La ad Tõnd welsa Alkʋrãan-kãng pʋgã bilgr buudã fãa n wĩnig nebã, la ninsaal yɩɩme n yɩɩd bũmbã fãa ne no-koεεmã."
  18,55,"Lɑ bũmb pa gɩdg nebã tɩ b kõ sɩda kãndgrã sẽn wa n wa-b la b kos b Soabã t'A yaaf-bɑ, yɑɑ b sẽn rat bɑl tɩ rãeenem rãmbã nɑ-kẽndrã wɑ bãmb me nengẽ wã, maa b wɑ yã nɑngã vẽenegã."
  18,56,"Lɑ Tõnd pa tʋmsd tẽn-tʋʋmbã rẽndame tɩ b yaa sũ-noogdb la bugsdba, la neb nins sẽn kɩflã maanda no-koεεm ne zĩri sẽn na yɩl n menes sɩdã ne rẽ, la b rɩk Mam Aaya-rãmbã (Alkʋrãanã) la b sẽn bugsd-b ne bũmb ningã n yɑɑndẽ."
  18,57,"Lɑ ãnd wẽgb n yɩɩd ned ning b sẽn tẽeg-ɑ ne Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã t'a gũd a zãn-kuidg la a yĩm a nus ɑ yiibã sẽn tʋm tɩ reng taoore, ad Tõnd ninga b sũyẽ wã lima, n kɩt tɩ b pa tõe n fahem-a (Alkʋrãanã) ye, la b tʋbẽ wã yẽdb n be beenẽ. Bɑ tɩ fo sã n boond-b n tʋgd kãndagr zĩigẽ, b pa na n tol n rɩk sor lɑe."
  18,58,"La fo Soabã yaa yaafg Naabã n yaa yolsg Soɑbɑ. A sã n rag n yõkd-b lame b tʋʋmã yĩnga, A rag n nɑ yãg ne-b ne sɩbgrã. Ka woto ye, ad b tara sεka, b kõn n tol n pɑɑm kõom zĩig n põs-ɑ ye."
  18,59,"Lɑ tẽn-kãensã Tõnd hɑlk-b lɑme, b sẽn wa n wẽgã, la Tõnd maana b halkrã tɩ tall sεka (raare)."
  18,60,"Lɑ (tẽeg) a Musa sẽn wa n yeel a sõgnã: "" mam pa na n bɑk n kẽnd hal n tʋg n tãag mog a yiibã yek-taabã zĩigẽ maɑ tɩ m kẽn zãmaan wooko""."
  18,61,"La b sẽn wa n ta mog a yiibã yek-taab zĩigã, b yĩma b zĩifã t'a rɩk a sorã mõgrã pʋgẽ n bɑsd wĩigɑ."
  18,62,"B sẽn wa n zʋʋgã, a yeela a sõgnã: "" tall d rɩɩbã n wa ne, ad Tõnd yãa d bob-kãngã pʋgẽ yɑɑms tεkẽ ."
  18,63,"[Tɩ sõgnã] yeele: "" fo yãame, tõnd sẽn wa n kɩll pĩigẽ wã, mam yĩma zĩifã la bũmb pɑ yĩms mɑɑm rẽndɑ ɑ Sʋtãan balɑ, tɩ mam pa togs foom ye,- ɑd a rɩkɑ ɑ sorã mogrã pʋgẽ tɩ yɑɑ yel-solemde""."
  18,64,"T'a [Musa] yeele :"" ad yaa rẽ la tõnd sẽn dɑ baoodã"". Tɩ b yiibã lebg n rik b nɑo wã vũun n tũnugdẽ."
  18,65,"Tɩ b yiibã tʋg n mik yɑmb sẽn yɩ Tõnd yamb sõmsã pʋgẽ D sẽn kõ-a yolsg sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ la D wĩnig-a bãngr sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ."
  18,66,"A Musa yeel-a lɑme:"" rẽ yĩnga m tõe n tũu foom sẽn na yɩl tɩ f wĩnig-m B sẽn wĩnig foom, sẽn yɑɑ kãndagrã?"""
  18,67,"La a yeele: ""ad fo ka na n tõog n maan sugr ne maam ye""."
  18,68,"F na n maana sugr wãn ne bũmb ning fo sẽn pa tar a bãngre?"""
  18,69,"La a [Musa] yeele: ''Wẽnd sã n sɑke fo na n mika maam tɩ m yaa sugr soaba, m ka na n kɩɩs foom yell me zug ye''."
  18,70,"La a yeele: "" fo sã n na n tũ maam, ra sok maam yell baa a yembr võor hal tɩ mam wa n togs foom a võorã""."
  18,71,"Tɩ b looge n tɩ tãɑg b sẽn nɑ n tɩ zomb koglgã t'a poog-a, t'a [Musa] yeele: "" fo poog-a lame n na n bõr a nebã bɩɩ? Ad fo wɑɑ ne yel-gẽengɑ!"""
  18,72,"La a yeele: ""rẽ yĩnga, mam pa reng n yeel foom tɩ f ka tõe n maan sugr ne maam?"""
  18,73,"La a [Musa] yeele: ""ra yõk maam m sẽn yĩm yĩng ye, la ra weoog maam m yellã pʋgẽ kãe-kãe ye''."
  18,74,"Tɩ b na n leb n tud n tɩ tãɑg b sẽn nɑ n yek biiga, t'a be ɑ kʋʋbẽ. T'a [Musa] yeele: "" fo kʋʋ yõor sẽn yaa yɩleng tɩ pa tũ ne yõor ye, ad fo wɑɑ ne yel sẽn kisi!"""
  18,75,"La a yeele: ""rẽ yĩnga, mam pa reng n yeel foom tɩ f ka nɑ n tol n tõog n maan sugr ne maam?"""
  18,76,"T'a Musa yeele: "" m sã n le sok foom bũmb a to yel-kãngã poorẽ, bɩ f ra le bas maam tɩ m pʋg-f ye, f taa padeng tεkẽ mam yellẽ wã""."
  18,77,"Tɩ b loog hɑl n wɑ tɩ ta tẽngẽ n bao rɩɩb tẽngã rãmb nengẽ tɩ b zãgs tɩ b kõn n reeg-b sãand ye; tɩ b yã lalg sẽn kɩll n rat n lʋɩ t'a maneg-a n me n yalse. La a [Musa] yeele: fo sã n rata f reegdɑ keoor a yĩngɑ""."
  18,78,"La a yeel-ɑ: "" wã la maam ne foom sʋk welgre, m na n wĩniga foom bũmb ning fo sẽn pa tõog n maan sugr ɑ poorẽ wã võore""."
  18,79,"La sã n ya ne koglgã, ra yaa nimbãɑn-neb rẽndɑ tɩ b tʋmd mogrã pʋga, tɩ m tʋll n na n ning-a zanga, bala naab n be b taoorã n reegd koglg sẽn yɑɑ sõmã fãa ne fãɑbo."
  18,80,"La sã n yaa ne bi-bilfã, a roagdb a yiibã yaa kõ-sɩd-rãmba, lɑ biigɑ nɑ n yii kɩfre ɑ kɑseng poorẽ, tɩ tõnd yaeesd t'a na n wa menesɑ b yiibã tɩ b kedg la b kɩfle b sẽn nongɑ keelem."
  18,81,"Tɩ tõnd tʋll tɩ b Soabã tedg n kõ b yiibã bi-sõng sẽn yɩɩd yẽ yɩlgrẽ n leb n pẽ n yɩɩd ne ɑ nɑ yols ɑ roɑgdb ɑ yiibã."
  18,82,"La sã n yaa ne lalgã, ra yaa tẽngã pʋg kom-dibli ɑ yiib sẽn yɑ kɩɩbs rẽndɑ, tɩ b arzεk n da be lalgã tẽngre; la b saambã yɩɩ nin-sõngo, tɩ fo Soabã tʋll tɩ b lebg kãsembɑ n buk b arzεkã. Woto yaa yolsg sẽn yi fo Soabã nengẽ, lɑ mam pa maan yel-kãensã ne m raab ye, yaa woto la bũmb ning fo sẽn pa tõog n maan sugr ne-ɑ wã welsgo""."
  18,83,"La b sokda foom a ZulƘarnayn yelle. Yeele: "" m na wa n karem n togs yãmb a kɩbare""."
  18,84,"Ad Tõnd kõ-a-la pãng la tõog tẽn-gãngã zugu, la D rɩk bũmbã fãa gill ɑ sẽn tʋll-ɑ sabab n kõ-a t'ɑ tɑ ɑ rɑɑbẽ wã."
  18,85,"T'a rɩk sababã n tʋg wĩnto-lʋɩtgẽ wã sẽn na yɩl n tɑ ɑ rɑɑbẽ wã."
  18,86,"Hal t'a tɩ ta wĩntoog sẽn lʋɩtẽ, ɑ mik-ɑ lɑme t'a lʋɩta ko-nif tʋʋlgẽ la a mikɑ neb beenẽ sẽn yɑɑ kɩfr-dãmbɑ, tɩ Tõnd yeele:"" Zulkarnayni maa tɩ fo sɩbg-ba maa f maan-b neere."
  18,87,"La a yeel yã: ""ned ning sẽn wẽg-a d na n namsɑ a soabã, la d lebs-a a Soabã nengẽ t'A tɩ nams-a ne nong sẽn yaa kεgenga''."
  18,88,"La sã n ya ned ning sẽn kõ-a sɩd la a tʋm sẽn sõmbe, ɑ tɑrɑ keoor sẽn yɑɑ ɑrzẽn, D na n yeel-ɑ lɑ tõnd sɑglsẽ wã sẽn yɑɑ yol-yole."
  18,89,"Rẽ poorẽ t'a leb n rɩk sor ɑ to n tũ sababã n tʋg wĩntoog sẽn pukdẽ."
  18,90,"Hal t'a sẽn wɑ n tɑ wĩntoogã pʋkrẽ wã, ɑ mikɑme tɩ ɑ pukdɑ neb zug Tõnd sẽn kɑ ning lill bãmb ne wĩntoogã sʋk ye."
  18,91,"Yaa woto lɑ ɑ yellã, lɑ ɑd Tõnd minimã gũbgɑ bũmb ning sẽn be a nengẽ wã."
  18,92,"Rẽ poorẽ t'a leb n dɩk sor ɑ to n tũ sababã."
  18,93,"Hal t'a tʋg n ta tãeens a yiibã geoong sʋka, n tɩ mik zãma sẽn pa tʋllẽ n fahem nin-zẽmes goam ye."
  18,94,"La b yeel yã: "" Zulkarnayni, ad a Yaaguug la a Maaguug maanda sãang tẽngã zugu, lɑ rẽ yĩngɑ tõnd tõe n yaoo foom sẽn na yɩl tɩ fo maan gɩdr tõnd ne bãmb sʋkã?"""
  18,95,"T'a yeele: ""mam Soabã sẽn kõ maam tõog la pãng ningã sõmblem n yɩɩd ligd fãɑ yãmb sẽn kõt mɑɑm, bi y sõng-y maam ne pãnga, tɩ m maan gɩdr yãmb ne b sʋka."
  18,96,"Wa-y ne kud-gɩrsã, hɑl t'ɑ ɑ sẽn wa n me n yek tãees a yiibã tɩ zems tɑɑbɑ, a yeelame: ""zug-y-yã"". Hal t'a sẽn n wɑ n lebg bugmã ɑ yeelɑme: "" wa-y ne zũud tɩ m kiig ɑ zug""."
  18,97,"B pa tõog n gãndg-ɑ, b pa tõog n poog n yi me ye."
  18,98,"La a yeelyã: ''woto yaa mam Soabã yolsgo, la mam Soabã pʋleng sã n wɑ wa, A maand-a lame t'a lʋɩ n sãeege; lɑ mam Soabã pʋleng yɩɩme n yaa sɩda''."
  18,99,"Lɑ D bas-b bõn-nɑɑndsã sãndɑ tɩ b fãood taab ra-kãng rɑɑrã sẽn yɑɑ zãmɑɑnɑ pɑɑsgẽ wã ; tɩ b fʋʋs bargẽ wã tɩ D tigim-b tiging tεkẽ n nɑ n geel-bɑ."
  18,100,"La D puk Gεhannem bugmã rɑ-kãng rɑɑrã n wĩng kɩfr-rãmbã pukr tεkẽ."
  18,101,"Neb nins nin sẽn da be lill pʋgẽ n yi Mɑm yʋʋrã tẽegrã, lɑ b rɑ yɩ n da ka tõe n kelg Wẽnd Aɑyɑyã ye."
  18,102,"Rẽ yĩnga neb nins sẽn kɩflã tẽedame tɩ b na n gãda Mam yemsã n maan lall-n-taas zẽng sẽn pa Maam? Ad Tõnd sεglɑ Gεhannem kɩfr-rãmbã yĩngɑ, tɩ yaa b sigb zĩiga."
  18,103,"Yeele:"" rẽ yĩnga m wĩnig yãmb neb nins sẽn yɩɩd bõn b tʋʋm pʋg bɩ?"""
  18,104,"Yaa neb nins b tʋʋmã dũni wã pʋgẽ wã sẽn menem n bɑs-b yikrã rɑɑrã tɩ b rãmbã yaool n tẽed tɩ b tʋmda tʋʋm-sõms sẽn nɑ n wɑ nɑf-bɑ."
  18,105,"Bãmb yaa neb sẽn kɩɩs b Soabã Aaya-rãmb la A yekrã, tɩ b tʋʋmã lʋɩ , rẽnd D ka na n fɑ-b dũni yikr rɑɑrã ye."
  18,106,"Yaa woto tɩ b rolb yɑɑ gεhɑnnɑm, b sẽn kɩflã la b rɩk Mam Aaya-rãmbã la M tẽn-tʋʋmbã tɩ yaa wɩsgã yĩnga."
  18,107,"Ad neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã la b tʋm tʋʋm-sõmã wã, arzãn na-tẽngã la b zĩndg zĩiga."
  18,108,"B yɑɑ pɑɑdb a pʋgẽ, b pa baood tedgr n nɑ bɑs-ɑ ye."
  18,109,"Yeele:""mogrã sã n da yaa rʋba, tɩ b na n tall-a n gʋls m Soabã koeesã, mogrã na sε, taoor tɩ m Soabã koeesã ka sε ye, baa tɩ Tõnd sã n wa ne mogã buud n pɑɑse""."
  18,110,"Yeele:"" ad mam yaa ned wa yãmb bilgri, tɩ b tʋmd wahɩ tɩ wat mam nengẽ, tɩ ɑd yãmb Soabã yaa Soɑb yεng, lɑ ned ning sẽn tẽed a Soabã sεgbã, bɩ a tʋm tʋʋm-sõma la a ra maan lagem-n-taar ne a Soabã baa fʋɩ ye""."
